1
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,080
My lord!

2
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:10,139
Please give us a few more days.

3
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,300
Our village

4
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,680
has absolutely no surplus grain left.

5
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,400
None?

6
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,820
Then you will pay with your heads.

7
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:17,280
Men!

8
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:20,200
Take everyone in the village away,

9
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,000
except the women over 60.

10
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:25,860
My lord!

11
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:27,540
My lord!

12
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:28,600
My lord!

13
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:30,680
Stop!

14
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,600
Let him go!

15
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,000
Stop!

16
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,600
Let him go!

17
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:36,760
I said let him go!

18
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,079
You can't take this!

19
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,530
Finding helpers

20
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,000
to go against me,

21
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:49,800
have you thought through the consequences?

22
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:50,960
It's a misunderstanding, my lord!

23
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,160
A misunderstanding!

24
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,120
Misunderstanding!

25
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,579
It's a misunderstanding!

26
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,760
Let all things sink,

27
00:02:58,760 --> 00:03:00,160
and roots lock the light.

28
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,240
Catch this boy playing tricks!

29
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,720
Did you find it?

30
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,600
I...

31
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:45,360
has been entrenched in Er City for several years.

32
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,620
Whoever enters Er City

33
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,280
has never been let out.

34
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,160
But as for that Golden Immortal,

35
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,140
there is still no trace of him.

36
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,960
Reporting to Lady Tu.

37
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,640
Over the past few months,

38
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,000
anyone...

39
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:01,240
who passed by Leiting Mountain,

40
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,760
I didn't miss a single one.

41
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,400
I checked them all thoroughly.

42
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,160
But...

43
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:13,680
As two of my Four Demons of Tumen,

44
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,920
you naturally need to achieve some merits.

45
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,560
I haven't given you much to do.

46
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,320
If you can't wait for him,

47
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,400
go find him.

48
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,500
If you still can't find him...

49
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,400
We will do our best to search for him.

50
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,330
We will not betray Lady Tu's trust.

51
00:04:45,159 --> 00:04:47,040
That banished Golden Immortal of Sanshanliu

52
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,080
is a rare encounter in ten thousand years.

53
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,159
If I find him

54
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,760
and enjoy his divine power,

55
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,360
I can ascend to immortality.

56
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:56,020
With such a good thing,

57
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:59,500
why bother undergoing tribulations and cultivating?

58
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:02,240
You must put more effort into helping me.

59
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,920
If I attain the Dao,

60
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,400
your cultivation

61
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:09,020
will surely advance by leaps and bounds.

62
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,560
Joining the immortal ranks

63
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,020
is just around the corner.

64
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:16,880
We will certainly lay down our lives for Lady Tu.

65
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,370
The same goes for me.

66
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:19,290
Lei Long,

67
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,660
serving under Lady Tu,

68
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,700
you must be completely loyal.

69
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,780
Please rest assured, Senior.

70
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,620
Please rest assured, Lady Tu.

71
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:29,920
Alright.

72
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:31,480
You may go.

73
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,960
Lady Tu,

74
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,770
relying on these two fools,

75
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,480
it will be hard to find the Golden Immortal.

76
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,600
Even ants can be used as medicine.

77
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,400
Give them one more chance.

78
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,520
You two,

79
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,200
go find some clues as well.

80
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:57,180
If we can't find the Golden Immortal,

81
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,840
no one will have peace.

82
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:11,800
Boss!

83
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:13,000
Boss, bad news!

84
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,560
Boss,

85
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:14,800
bad news!

86
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:15,320
Boss!

87
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,850
Why did you come back alone?

88
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,800
Didn't you go to Qinghe Village?

89
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:19,900
Where is Niu Yidao?

90
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:22,120
We did arrive at Qinghe Village.

91
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,440
I was keeping watch from a distance at the time.

92
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:25,170
That's how I managed to escape.

93
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,040
Except for me,

94
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,170
all the brothers

95
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,240
were killed.

96
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,080
You mean

97
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:33,080
a monster?

98
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,600
In an instant,

99
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,490
he burned

100
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,180
all the brothers to death.

101
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,760
It must be a monster.

102
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:40,280
Recently, people have often

103
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,920
been taken away and eaten by monsters.

104
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,720
It must be him.

105
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,800
Let's go avenge the second boss, Niu.

106
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,960
Damn monster.

107
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:48,090
We must cut him into a thousand pieces.

108
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:49,560
Boss.

109
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,160
Boys,

110
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,280
let's go.

111
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,920
Let's go meet this so-called monster.

112
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,760
Let's head out!

113
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,240
Village Chief,

114
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,160
I didn't lie to you, did I?

115
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,820
This master is very powerful.

116
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,920
These are just small fry.

117
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:33,600
If the bandit leader Lei Long comes down to seek revenge,

118
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,440
none of us will survive.

119
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,159
Village Chief,

120
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:37,000
with the master being so powerful,

121
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,159
why should we fear Lei Long?

122
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,090
What do you know?

123
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:41,920
He might be fine dealing with these little bandits,

124
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,760
but Lei Long is no ordinary man.

125
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,080
I've seen it with my own eyes.

126
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:47,610
He lifted a rock weighing over a thousand jin.

127
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,159
You said

128
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,680
he can lift stones weighing thousands of pounds.

129
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,800
Hurry up and leave.

130
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,440
When Leilong arrives,

131
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:57,200
we'll cut ties with you.

132
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,280
Then we'll beg him,

133
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:03,000
and maybe we'll still have a chance to survive.

134
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,660
You want to survive on other people's sympathy?

135
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,100
What else can we do?

136
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,600
Look at people like us.

137
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:16,000
How can we have the skills to survive?

138
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,440
The skills to survive

139
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,020
must be fought for by yourselves.

140
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,680
Before,

141
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,840
you had no chance.

142
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,360
But today I am here,

143
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,170
so you have a chance.

144
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:27,880
Even so,

145
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:31,240
are you unwilling to fight for it?

146
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,520
Our village's fate

147
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,159
is just like this.

148
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,799
If you really want to help us,

149
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:39,090
then you should leave quickly.

150
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,140
Master.

151
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,570
I have no money, Master.

152
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,100
This is for you,

153
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,040
to protect yourself.

154
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,900
Courage is not fearlessness.

155
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,800
If you can face fear without retreating

156
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,130
and fight for survival,

157
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:06,650
only then can you find a chance of survival

158
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,480
and gain the blessing of Heaven.

159
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,210
Xinyang flower.

160
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:13,840
Feilu.

161
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,380
They're here already.

162
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,280
Where is he?

163
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,800
Lord Leilong,

164
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:32,620
that man has already left.

165
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,600
We don't know him at all.

166
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,400
It was that man

167
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,800
who clashed with your men

168
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,050
and started a fight.

169
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,650
It has nothing to do with us.

170
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,770
Nothing to do with us at all.

171
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,640
Nothing to do with you?

172
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:44,680
Yes.

173
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,360
Look,

174
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,520
how could we dare to offend your men?

175
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,440
Here.

176
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:52,240
Boss Lei.

177
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,120
Look,

178
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,240
this is the only food our village has left,

179
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,200
and we're giving it all to you.

180
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,000
Please calm down.

181
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,240
Calm down, Boss Lei.

182
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:58,920
Calm down.

183
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,440
Please calm down.

184
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,080
Boss Lei.

185
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,720
Kill them all.

186
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,970
Let them accompany our dead brothers.

187
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,280
Stop!

188
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,400
Your Qinghe Village

189
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,900
actually produced someone with a backbone.

190
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,130
Little brother,

191
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,720
what are you trying to do?

192
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,690
All of you, stop!

193
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,520
Why should we let them go?

194
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,320
Don't come any closer.

195
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,040
I'll shoot.

196
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,360
Jieqiang Haihui
